        "message": "It's Monday 9:00 AM, time for weekly workspace backup. Please execute: powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"C:\\Users\\WH\\.openclaw\\workspace-assistant\\scripts\\weekly-backup-en.ps1\" This will: 1. Backup both workspace directories; 2. Generate backup report; 3. Clean old backups; 4. Send Feishu notification. Backup location: C:\\Users\\WH\\.openclaw\\backups\\"
